\v 16 a goat to be sacrificed to remove people’s guilt for their sins,
\v 17 as well as two cattle, five male sheep, five male goats, and five one-year-old male lambs to be sacrificed for maintaining fellowship {with Yahweh}. All these are what Nahshon son of Amminadab gave.

